32p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
33
34}
35;e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_Integer, &l);

43int ASN1CALL
44decode_Version(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, Version *data, size_t *size)
45{
46size_t ret = 0;
47size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
48int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
49
50memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
51{
52size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
53Der_type Top_type;
54e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Integer, &Top_datalen, &l);
55if (e == 0 && Top_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
56if(e) goto fail;
57p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
58Top_oldlen = len;
59if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
60len = Top_datalen;
61{
62int enumint;
63e = der_get_integer(p, len, &enumint, &l);
64if(e) goto fail;
65p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
66*data = enumint;
67}
68len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
69}
70if(size) *size = ret;
71return 0;
72fail:
73free_Version(data);
74return e;
75}

83length_Version(const Version *data)
84{
85size_t ret = 0;
86{
87int enumint = *data;
88ret += der_length_integer(&enumint);
89}
90ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
91return ret;

324int ASN1CALL
325encode_AlgorithmIdentifier(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const AlgorithmIdentifier *data, size_t *size)
326{
327size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
328size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
329int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
330
331/* parameters */
332if((data)->parameters) {
333size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
334ret = 0;
335e = encode_heim_any(p, len, (data)->parameters, &l);
336if (e) return e;
337p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
338
339ret += Top_tag_oldret;
340}
341/* algorithm */
342{
343size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
344ret = 0;
345e = der_put_oid(p, len, &(data)->algorithm, &l);
346if (e) return e;
347p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
348
349e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_OID, &l);
350if (e) return e;
351p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
352
353ret += Top_tag_oldret;
354}
355e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, &l);
356if (e) return e;
357p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
358
359*size = ret;
360return 0;
361}

363int ASN1CALL
364decode_AlgorithmIdentifier(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, AlgorithmIdentifier *data, size_t *size)
365{
366size_t ret = 0;
367size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
368int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
369
370memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
371{
372size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
373Der_type Top_type;
374e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
375if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
376if(e) goto fail;
377p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
378Top_oldlen = len;
379if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
380len = Top_datalen;
381{
382size_t algorithm_datalen, algorithm_oldlen;
383Der_type algorithm_type;
384e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &algorithm_type, UT_OID, &algorithm_datalen, &l);
385if (e == 0 && algorithm_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
386if(e) goto fail;
387p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
388algorithm_oldlen = len;
389if (algorithm_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
390len = algorithm_datalen;
391e = der_get_oid(p, len, &(data)->algorithm, &l);
392if(e) goto fail;
393p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
394len = algorithm_oldlen - algorithm_datalen;
395}
396(data)->parameters = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->parameters));
397if ((data)->parameters == NULL) goto fail;
398e = decode_heim_any(p, len, (data)->parameters, &l);
399if(e) {
400free((data)->parameters);
401(data)->parameters = NULL;
402} else {
403p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
404}
405len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
406}
407if(size) *size = ret;
408return 0;
409fail:
410free_AlgorithmIdentifier(data);
411return e;
412}
413
414void ASN1CALL
415free_AlgorithmIdentifier(AlgorithmIdentifier *data)
416{
417der_free_oid(&(data)->algorithm);
418if((data)->parameters) {
419free_heim_any((data)->parameters);
420free((data)->parameters);
421(data)->parameters = NULL;
422}
423}
424
425size_t ASN1CALL
426length_AlgorithmIdentifier(const AlgorithmIdentifier *data)
427{
428size_t ret = 0;
429{
430size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
431ret = 0;
432ret += der_length_oid(&(data)->algorithm);
433ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
434ret += Top_tag_oldret;
435}
436if((data)->parameters){
437size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
438ret = 0;
439ret += length_heim_any((data)->parameters);
440ret += Top_tag_oldret;
441}
442ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
443return ret;
444}
445
446int ASN1CALL
447copy_AlgorithmIdentifier(const AlgorithmIdentifier *from, AlgorithmIdentifier *to)
448{
449memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
450if(der_copy_oid(&(from)->algorithm, &(to)->algorithm)) goto fail;
451if((from)->parameters) {
452(to)->parameters = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->parameters));
453if((to)->parameters == NULL) goto fail;
454if(copy_heim_any((from)->parameters, (to)->parameters)) goto fail;
455}else
456(to)->parameters = NULL;
457return 0;
458fail:
459free_AlgorithmIdentifier(to);
460return ENOMEM;
461}

478*size = ret;
479return 0;
480}

713}
714else if (der_match_tag(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_TeletexString, NULL) == 0) {
715{

718e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &teletexString_type, UT_TeletexString, &teletexString_datalen, &l);
719if (e == 0 && teletexString_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }

726if(e) goto fail;
727p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
728len = teletexString_oldlen - teletexString_datalen;
729}
730(data)->element = choice_DirectoryString_teletexString;
731}
732else if (der_match_tag(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_PrintableString, NULL) == 0) {
733{
734size_t printableString_datalen, printableString_oldlen;
735Der_type printableString_type;
736e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &printableString_type, UT_PrintableString, &printableString_datalen, &l);
737if (e == 0 && printableString_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }

744if(e) goto fail;
745p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
746len = printableString_oldlen - printableString_datalen;
747}
748(data)->element = choice_DirectoryString_printableString;
749}
750else if (der_match_tag(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_GraphicString, NULL) == 0) {
751{
752size_t universalString_datalen, universalString_oldlen;
753Der_type universalString_type;
754e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &universalString_type, UT_GraphicString, &universalString_datalen, &l);
755if (e == 0 && universalString_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
756if(e) goto fail;

762if(e) goto fail;

764len = universalString_oldlen - universalString_datalen;

768else if (der_match_tag(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_UTF8String, NULL) == 0) {

774if(e) goto fail;
775p += l; len -= l; ret += l;

777if (utf8String_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
778len = utf8String_datalen;
779e = der_get_utf8string(p, len, &(data)->u.utf8String, &l);
780if(e) goto fail;
781p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
782len = utf8String_oldlen - utf8String_datalen;
783}
784(data)->element = choice_DirectoryString_utf8String;
785}
786else if (der_match_tag(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_BMPString, NULL) == 0) {
787{
788size_t bmpString_datalen, bmpString_oldlen;
789Der_type bmpString_type;
790e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &bmpString_type, UT_BMPString, &bmpString_datalen, &l);

804else {
805e = ASN1_PARSE_ERROR;

807}
808if(size) *size = ret;
809return 0;
810fail:
811free_DirectoryString(data);
812return e;
813}

815void ASN1CALL
816free_DirectoryString(DirectoryString *data)
817{
818switch((data)->element) {
819case choice_DirectoryString_ia5String:
820der_free_ia5_string(&(data)->u.ia5String);
821break;
822case choice_DirectoryString_teletexString:
823der_free_general_string(&(data)->u.teletexString);
824break;
825case choice_DirectoryString_printableString:
826der_free_printable_string(&(data)->u.printableString);
827break;
828case choice_DirectoryString_universalString:
829der_free_universal_string(&(data)->u.universalString);
830break;
831case choice_DirectoryString_utf8String:
832der_free_utf8string(&(data)->u.utf8String);
833break;
834case choice_DirectoryString_bmpString:
835der_free_bmp_string(&(data)->u.bmpString);
836break;
837}
838}

840size_t ASN1CALL
841length_DirectoryString(const DirectoryString *data)
842{
843size_t ret = 0;
844switch((data)->element) {
845case choice_DirectoryString_ia5String:
846{
847size_t Top_oldret = ret;
848ret = 0;
849ret += der_length_ia5_string(&(data)->u.ia5String);
850ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
851ret += Top_oldret;
852}
853break;
854case choice_DirectoryString_teletexString:
855{
856size_t Top_oldret = ret;
857ret = 0;
858ret += der_length_general_string(&(data)->u.teletexString);
859ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
860ret += Top_oldret;
861}
862break;
863case choice_DirectoryString_printableString:
864{
865size_t Top_oldret = ret;
866ret = 0;
867ret += der_length_printable_string(&(data)->u.printableString);
868ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
869ret += Top_oldret;
870}
871break;
872case choice_DirectoryString_universalString:
873{
874size_t Top_oldret = ret;
875ret = 0;
876ret += der_length_universal_string(&(data)->u.universalString);
877ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
878ret += Top_oldret;
879}
880break;
881case choice_DirectoryString_utf8String:
882{
883size_t Top_oldret = ret;
884ret = 0;
885ret += der_length_utf8string(&(data)->u.utf8String);
886ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
887ret += Top_oldret;
888}
889break;
890case choice_DirectoryString_bmpString:
891{
892size_t Top_oldret = ret;
893ret = 0;
894ret += der_length_bmp_string(&(data)->u.bmpString);
895ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
896ret += Top_oldret;
897}
898break;
899}
900return ret;
901}

903int ASN1CALL
904copy_DirectoryString(const DirectoryString *from, DirectoryString *to)
905{
906memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
907(to)->element = (from)->element;
908switch((from)->element) {
909case choice_DirectoryString_ia5String:
910if(der_copy_ia5_string(&(from)->u.ia5String, &(to)->u.ia5String)) goto fail;
911break;
912case choice_DirectoryString_teletexString:
913if(der_copy_general_string(&(from)->u.teletexString, &(to)->u.teletexString)) goto fail;
914break;
915case choice_DirectoryString_printableString:
916if(der_copy_printable_string(&(from)->u.printableString, &(to)->u.printableString)) goto fail;
917break;
918case choice_DirectoryString_universalString:
919if(der_copy_universal_string(&(from)->u.universalString, &(to)->u.universalString)) goto fail;
920break;
921case choice_DirectoryString_utf8String:
922if(der_copy_utf8string(&(from)->u.utf8String, &(to)->u.utf8String)) goto fail;
923break;
924case choice_DirectoryString_bmpString:
925if(der_copy_bmp_string(&(from)->u.bmpString, &(to)->u.bmpString)) goto fail;
926break;
927}
928return 0;
929fail:
930free_DirectoryString(to);
931return ENOMEM;
932}
933
934int ASN1CALL
935encode_Attribute(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const Attribute *data, size_t *size)
936{
937size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
938size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
939int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
940
941/* value */
942{
943size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
944ret = 0;
945{
946heim_octet_string *val;
947size_t elen = 0, totallen = 0;
948int eret = 0;
949if ((&(data)->value)->len > UINT_MAX/sizeof(val[0]))
950return ERANGE;
951val = malloc(sizeof(val[0]) * (&(data)->value)->len);
952if (val == NULL && (&(data)->value)->len != 0) return ENOMEM;
953for(i = 0; i < (int)(&(data)->value)->len; i++) {
954ASN1_MALLOC_ENCODE(heim_any, val[i].data, val[i].length, &(&(data)->value)->val[i], &elen, eret);
955if(eret) {
956i--;
957while (i >= 0) {
958free(val[i].data);
959i--;
960}
961free(val);
962return eret;
963}
964totallen += elen;
965}
966if (totallen > len) {
967for (i = 0; i < (int)(&(data)->value)->len; i++) {
968free(val[i].data);
969}
970free(val);
971return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
972}
973qsort(val, (&(data)->value)->len, sizeof(val[0]), _heim_der_set_sort);
974for(i = (int)(&(data)->value)->len - 1; i >= 0; --i) {
975p -= val[i].length;
976ret += val[i].length;
977memcpy(p + 1, val[i].data, val[i].length);
978free(val[i].data);
979}
980free(val);
981}
982e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Set, &l);
983if (e) return e;
984p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
985
986ret += Top_tag_oldret;
987}
988/* type */
989{
990size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
991ret = 0;
992e = encode_AttributeType(p, len, &(data)->type, &l);
993if (e) return e;
994p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
995
996ret += Top_tag_oldret;
997}
998e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, &l);
999if (e) return e;
1000p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
1001
1002*size = ret;
1003return 0;
1004}
1005
1006int ASN1CALL
1007decode_Attribute(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, Attribute *data, size_t *size)
1008{
1009size_t ret = 0;
1010size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1011int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1012
1013memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
1014{
1015size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
1016Der_type Top_type;
1017e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
1018if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
1019if(e) goto fail;
1020p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1021Top_oldlen = len;
1022if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
1023len = Top_datalen;
1024e = decode_AttributeType(p, len, &(data)->type, &l);
1025if(e) goto fail;
1026p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1027{
1028size_t value_datalen, value_oldlen;
1029Der_type value_type;
1030e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &value_type, UT_Set, &value_datalen, &l);
1031if (e == 0 && value_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
1032if(e) goto fail;
1033p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1034value_oldlen = len;
1035if (value_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
1036len = value_datalen;
1037{
1038size_t value_Tag_origlen = len;
1039size_t value_Tag_oldret = ret;
1040size_t value_Tag_olen = 0;
1041void *value_Tag_tmp;
1042ret = 0;
1043(&(data)->value)->len = 0;
1044(&(data)->value)->val = NULL;
1045while(ret < value_Tag_origlen) {
1046size_t value_Tag_nlen = value_Tag_olen + sizeof(*((&(data)->value)->val));
1047if (value_Tag_olen > value_Tag_nlen) { e = ASN1_OVERFLOW; goto fail; }
1048value_Tag_olen = value_Tag_nlen;
1049value_Tag_tmp = realloc((&(data)->value)->val, value_Tag_olen);
1050if (value_Tag_tmp == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
1051(&(data)->value)->val = value_Tag_tmp;
1052e = decode_heim_any(p, len, &(&(data)->value)->val[(&(data)->value)->len], &l);
1053if(e) goto fail;
1054p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1055(&(data)->value)->len++;
1056len = value_Tag_origlen - ret;
1057}
1058ret += value_Tag_oldret;
1059}
1060len = value_oldlen - value_datalen;
1061}
1062len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
1063}
1064if(size) *size = ret;
1065return 0;
1066fail:
1067free_Attribute(data);
1068return e;
1069}
1070
1071void ASN1CALL
1072free_Attribute(Attribute *data)
1073{
1074free_AttributeType(&(data)->type);
1075while((&(data)->value)->len){
1076free_heim_any(&(&(data)->value)->val[(&(data)->value)->len-1]);
1077(&(data)->value)->len--;
1078}
1079free((&(data)->value)->val);
1080(&(data)->value)->val = NULL;
1081}

1083size_t ASN1CALL
1084length_Attribute(const Attribute *data)
1085{
1086size_t ret = 0;
1087{
1088size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
1089ret = 0;
1090ret += length_AttributeType(&(data)->type);
1091ret += Top_tag_oldret;
1092}
1093{
1094size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
1095ret = 0;
1096{
1097size_t value_tag_oldret = ret;
1098unsigned int n_value_tag;
1099ret = 0;
1100for(n_value_tag = (&(data)->value)->len; n_value_tag > 0; --n_value_tag){
1101size_t value_tag_for_oldret = ret;
1102ret = 0;
1103ret += length_heim_any(&(&(data)->value)->val[n_value_tag - 1]);
1104ret += value_tag_for_oldret;
1105}
1106ret += value_tag_oldret;
1107}
1108ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
1109ret += Top_tag_oldret;
1110}
1111ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
1112return ret;
1113}

1116copy_Attribute(const Attribute *from, Attribute *to)
1117{
1118memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
1119if(copy_AttributeType(&(from)->type, &(to)->type)) goto fail;
1120if(((&(to)->value)->val = malloc((&(from)->value)->len * sizeof(*(&(to)->value)->val))) == NULL && (&(from)->value)->len != 0)
1121goto fail;
1122for((&(to)->value)->len = 0; (&(to)->value)->len < (&(from)->value)->len; (&(to)->value)->len++){
1123if(copy_heim_any(&(&(from)->value)->val[(&(to)->value)->len], &(&(to)->value)->val[(&(to)->value)->len])) goto fail;
1124}
1125return 0;
1126fail:
1127free_Attribute(to);
1128return ENOMEM;
1129}

1238int ASN1CALL
1239encode_RelativeDistinguishedName(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const RelativeDistinguishedName *data, size_t *size)
1240{
1241size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
1242size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1243int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1244
1245{
1246heim_octet_string *val;
1247size_t elen = 0, totallen = 0;
1248int eret = 0;
1249if ((data)->len > UINT_MAX/sizeof(val[0]))
1250return ERANGE;
1251val = malloc(sizeof(val[0]) * (data)->len);
1252if (val == NULL && (data)->len != 0) return ENOMEM;
1253for(i = 0; i < (int)(data)->len; i++) {
1254ASN1_MALLOC_ENCODE(AttributeTypeAndValue, val[i].data, val[i].length, &(data)->val[i], &elen, eret);
1255if(eret) {
1256i--;
1257while (i >= 0) {
1258free(val[i].data);
1259i--;
1260}
1261free(val);
1262return eret;
1263}
1264totallen += elen;
1265}
1266if (totallen > len) {
1267for (i = 0; i < (int)(data)->len; i++) {
1268free(val[i].data);
1269}
1270free(val);
1271return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
1272}
1273qsort(val, (data)->len, sizeof(val[0]), _heim_der_set_sort);
1274for(i = (int)(data)->len - 1; i >= 0; --i) {
1275p -= val[i].length;
1276ret += val[i].length;
1277memcpy(p + 1, val[i].data, val[i].length);
1278free(val[i].data);
1279}
1280free(val);
1281}
1282e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Set, &l);
1283if (e) return e;
1284p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
1285
1286*size = ret;
1287return 0;
1288}

1529int ASN1CALL
1530decode_Name(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, Name *data, size_t *size)
1531{
1532size_t ret = 0;
1533size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1534int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1535const unsigned char *begin = p;
1536
1537memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
1538if (der_match_tag(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, NULL) == 0) {
1539e = decode_RDNSequence(p, len, &(data)->u.rdnSequence, &l);
1540if(e) goto fail;
1541p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1542(data)->element = choice_Name_rdnSequence;
1543}
1544else {
1545e = ASN1_PARSE_ERROR;
1546goto fail;
1547}
1548data->_save.data = calloc(1, ret);
1549if (data->_save.data == NULL) {
1550e = ENOMEM; goto fail;
1551}
1552data->_save.length = ret;
1553memcpy(data->_save.data, begin, ret);
1554if(size) *size = ret;
1555return 0;
1556fail:
1557free_Name(data);
1558return e;
1559}

1593{ int ret;
1594ret = der_copy_octet_string(&(from)->_save, &(to)->_save);
1595if (ret) goto fail;
1596}
1597(to)->element = (from)->element;
1598switch((from)->element) {
1599case choice_Name_rdnSequence:
1600if(copy_RDNSequence(&(from)->u.rdnSequence, &(to)->u.rdnSequence)) goto fail;
1601break;
1602}
1603return 0;
1604fail:
1605free_Name(to);
1606return ENOMEM;
1607}

1684int ASN1CALL
1685encode_Time(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const Time *data, size_t *size)
1686{
1687size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
1688size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1689int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1690
1691
1692switch((data)->element) {
1693case choice_Time_generalTime: {size_t Top_oldret = ret;
1694ret = 0;
1695e = der_put_generalized_time(p, len, &((data))->u.generalTime, &l);
1696if (e) return e;
1697p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
1698
1699e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_GeneralizedTime, &l);
1700if (e) return e;
1701p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
1702
1703ret += Top_oldret;
1704break;
1705}
1706case choice_Time_utcTime: {size_t Top_oldret = ret;
1707ret = 0;
1708e = der_put_utctime(p, len, &((data))->u.utcTime, &l);
1709if (e) return e;
1710p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
1711
1712e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_UTCTime, &l);
1713if (e) return e;
1714p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
1715
1716ret += Top_oldret;
1717break;
1718}
1719};
1720*size = ret;
1721return 0;
1722}
1723
1724int ASN1CALL
1725decode_Time(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, Time *data, size_t *size)
1726{
1727size_t ret = 0;
1728size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1729int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1730
1731memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
1732if (der_match_tag(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_UTCTime, NULL) == 0) {
1733{
1734size_t utcTime_datalen, utcTime_oldlen;
1735Der_type utcTime_type;
1736e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &utcTime_type, UT_UTCTime, &utcTime_datalen, &l);
1737if (e == 0 && utcTime_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
1738if(e) goto fail;
1739p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1740utcTime_oldlen = len;
1741if (utcTime_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
1742len = utcTime_datalen;
1743e = der_get_utctime(p, len, &(data)->u.utcTime, &l);
1744if(e) goto fail;
1745p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1746len = utcTime_oldlen - utcTime_datalen;
1747}
1748(data)->element = choice_Time_utcTime;
1749}
1750else if (der_match_tag(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_GeneralizedTime, NULL) == 0) {
1751{
1752size_t generalTime_datalen, generalTime_oldlen;
1753Der_type generalTime_type;
1754e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &generalTime_type, UT_GeneralizedTime, &generalTime_datalen, &l);
1755if (e == 0 && generalTime_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
1756if(e) goto fail;
1757p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1758generalTime_oldlen = len;
1759if (generalTime_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
1760len = generalTime_datalen;
1761e = der_get_generalized_time(p, len, &(data)->u.generalTime, &l);
1762if(e) goto fail;
1763p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1764len = generalTime_oldlen - generalTime_datalen;
1765}
1766(data)->element = choice_Time_generalTime;
1767}
1768else {
1769e = ASN1_PARSE_ERROR;
1770goto fail;
1771}
1772if(size) *size = ret;
1773return 0;
1774fail:
1775free_Time(data);
1776return e;
1777}
1778
1779void ASN1CALL
1780free_Time(Time *data)
1781{
1782switch((data)->element) {
1783case choice_Time_utcTime:
1784break;
1785case choice_Time_generalTime:
1786break;
1787}
1788}
1789
1790size_t ASN1CALL
1791length_Time(const Time *data)
1792{
1793size_t ret = 0;
1794switch((data)->element) {
1795case choice_Time_utcTime:
1796{
1797size_t Top_oldret = ret;
1798ret = 0;
1799ret += der_length_utctime(&(data)->u.utcTime);
1800ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
1801ret += Top_oldret;
1802}
1803break;
1804case choice_Time_generalTime:
1805{
1806size_t Top_oldret = ret;
1807ret = 0;
1808ret += der_length_generalized_time(&(data)->u.generalTime);
1809ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
1810ret += Top_oldret;
1811}
1812break;
1813}
1814return ret;
1815}
1816
1817int ASN1CALL
1818copy_Time(const Time *from, Time *to)
1819{
1820memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
1821(to)->element = (from)->element;
1822switch((from)->element) {
1823case choice_Time_utcTime:
1824*(&(to)->u.utcTime) = *(&(from)->u.utcTime);
1825break;
1826case choice_Time_generalTime:
1827*(&(to)->u.generalTime) = *(&(from)->u.generalTime);
1828break;
1829}
1830return 0;
1831}

1868int ASN1CALL
1869decode_Validity(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, Validity *data, size_t *size)
1870{
1871size_t ret = 0;
1872size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1873int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
1874
1875memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
1876{
1877size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
1878Der_type Top_type;
1879e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
1880if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
1881if(e) goto fail;
1882p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1883Top_oldlen = len;

1887if(e) goto fail;
1888p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1889e = decode_Time(p, len, &(data)->notAfter, &l);
1890if(e) goto fail;
1891p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
1892len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
1893}
1894if(size) *size = ret;
1895return 0;
1896fail:

1898return e;
1899}

1924ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
1925return ret;

2200size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2201int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2202

2204{

2206Der_type Top_type;
2207e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
2208if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
2209if(e) goto fail;
2210p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2211Top_oldlen = len;
2212if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
2213len = Top_datalen;
2214{

2239p += l; len -= l; ret += l;

2260if(e) goto fail;

2263}
2264len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;

2285length_Extension(const Extension *data)
2286{

2293ret += Top_tag_oldret;

2296size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;

2298ret += 1;
2299ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
2300ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2301}

2304ret = 0;

2313int ASN1CALL
2314copy_Extension(const Extension *from, Extension *to)
2315{
2316memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
2317if(der_copy_oid(&(from)->extnID, &(to)->extnID)) goto fail;
2318if((from)->critical) {
2319(to)->critical = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->critical));
2320if((to)->critical == NULL) goto fail;
2321*((to)->critical) = *((from)->critical);
2322}else
2323(to)->critical = NULL;
2324if(der_copy_octet_string(&(from)->extnValue, &(to)->extnValue)) goto fail;
2325return 0;
2326fail:
2327free_Extension(to);
2328return ENOMEM;
2329}

2333{

2337

2339size_t Top_tag_for_oldret = ret;
2340ret = 0;

2344

2355int ASN1CALL
2356decode_Extensions(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, Extensions *data, size_t *size)
2357{
2358size_t ret = 0;
2359size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2360int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2361
2362memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
2363{
2364size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
2365Der_type Top_type;
2366e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
2367if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
2368if(e) goto fail;
2369p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2370Top_oldlen = len;
2371if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
2372len = Top_datalen;
2373{
2374size_t Top_Tag_origlen = len;
2375size_t Top_Tag_oldret = ret;
2376size_t Top_Tag_olen = 0;
2377void *Top_Tag_tmp;
2378ret = 0;
2379(data)->len = 0;
2380(data)->val = NULL;
2381while(ret < Top_Tag_origlen) {
2382size_t Top_Tag_nlen = Top_Tag_olen + sizeof(*((data)->val));
2383if (Top_Tag_olen > Top_Tag_nlen) { e = ASN1_OVERFLOW; goto fail; }
2384Top_Tag_olen = Top_Tag_nlen;
2385Top_Tag_tmp = realloc((data)->val, Top_Tag_olen);
2386if (Top_Tag_tmp == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
2387(data)->val = Top_Tag_tmp;
2388e = decode_Extension(p, len, &(data)->val[(data)->len], &l);
2389if(e) goto fail;
2390p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2391(data)->len++;
2392len = Top_Tag_origlen - ret;
2393}
2394ret += Top_Tag_oldret;
2395}
2396if ((data)->len > 2147483647) {
2397e = ASN1_MAX_CONSTRAINT; goto fail;
2398}
2399if ((data)->len < 1) {
2400e = ASN1_MIN_CONSTRAINT; goto fail;
2401}
2402len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
2403}
2404if(size) *size = ret;
2405return 0;
2406fail:
2407free_Extensions(data);
2408return e;
2409}

2411void ASN1CALL
2412free_Extensions(Extensions *data)
2413{
2414while((data)->len){
2415free_Extension(&(data)->val[(data)->len-1]);
2416(data)->len--;
2417}
2418free((data)->val);
2419(data)->val = NULL;
2420}

2422size_t ASN1CALL
2423length_Extensions(const Extensions *data)
2424{
2425size_t ret = 0;
2426{
2427size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
2428unsigned int n_Top_tag;
2429ret = 0;
2430for(n_Top_tag = (data)->len; n_Top_tag > 0; --n_Top_tag){
2431size_t Top_tag_for_oldret = ret;
2432ret = 0;
2433ret += length_Extension(&(data)->val[n_Top_tag - 1]);
2434ret += Top_tag_for_oldret;
2435}
2436ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2437}
2438ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
2439return ret;
2440}
2441
2442int ASN1CALL
2443copy_Extensions(const Extensions *from, Extensions *to)
2444{
2445memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
2446if(((to)->val = malloc((from)->len * sizeof(*(to)->val))) == NULL && (from)->len != 0)
2447goto fail;
2448for((to)->len = 0; (to)->len < (from)->len; (to)->len++){
2449if(copy_Extension(&(from)->val[(to)->len], &(to)->val[(to)->len])) goto fail;
2450}
2451return 0;
2452fail:
2453free_Extensions(to);
2454return ENOMEM;
2455}
2456
2457int ASN1CALL
2458add_Extensions(Extensions *data, const Extension *element)
2459{
2460int ret;
2461void *ptr;
2462
2463ptr = realloc(data->val,
2464 (data->len + 1) * sizeof(data->val[0]));
2465if (ptr == NULL) return ENOMEM;
2466data->val = ptr;
2467
2468ret = copy_Extension(element, &data->val[data->len]);
2469if (ret) return ret;
2470data->len++;
2471return 0;
2472}
2473
2474int ASN1CALL
2475remove_Extensions(Extensions *data, unsigned int element)
2476{
2477void *ptr;
2478
2479if (data->len == 0 || element >= data->len)
2480 return ASN1_OVERRUN;
2481free_Extension(&data->val[element]);
2482data->len--;
2483if (element < data->len)
2484 memmove(&data->val[element], &data->val[element + 1],
2485 sizeof(data->val[0]) * (data->len - element));
2486ptr = realloc(data->val, data->len * sizeof(data->val[0]));
2487if (ptr != NULL || data->len == 0) data->val = ptr;
2488return 0;
2489}

2491int ASN1CALL
2492encode_TBSCertificate(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const TBSCertificate *data, size_t *size)
2493{
2494size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
2495size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2496int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2497
2498/* extensions */
2499if((data)->extensions) {
2500size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2501ret = 0;
2502e = encode_Extensions(p, len, (data)->extensions, &l);
2503if (e) return e;
2504p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2505
2506e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, CONS, 3, &l);
2507if (e) return e;
2508p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2509
2510ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2511}
2512/* subjectUniqueID */
2513if((data)->subjectUniqueID) {
2514size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2515ret = 0;

2517if (e) return e;
2518p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2519
2520e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, PRIM, 2, &l);
2521if (e) return e;
2522p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2523
2524ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2525}
2526/* issuerUniqueID */
2527if((data)->issuerUniqueID) {
2528size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2529ret = 0;
2530e = der_put_bit_string(p, len, (data)->issuerUniqueID, &l);
2531if (e) return e;
2532p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2533
2534e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, PRIM, 1, &l);
2535if (e) return e;
2536p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2537
2538ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2539}
2540/* subjectPublicKeyInfo */
2541{
2542size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2543ret = 0;
2544e = encode_SubjectPublicKeyInfo(p, len, &(data)->subjectPublicKeyInfo, &l);
2545if (e) return e;
2546p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2547
2548ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2549}
2550/* subject */
2551{
2552size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2553ret = 0;
2554e = encode_Name(p, len, &(data)->subject, &l);
2555if (e) return e;
2556p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2557
2558ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2559}
2560/* validity */
2561{
2562size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2563ret = 0;
2564e = encode_Validity(p, len, &(data)->validity, &l);
2565if (e) return e;
2566p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2567
2568ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2569}
2570/* issuer */
2571{
2572size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2573ret = 0;
2574e = encode_Name(p, len, &(data)->issuer, &l);
2575if (e) return e;
2576p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2577
2578ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2579}
2580/* signature */
2581{
2582size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2583ret = 0;
2584e = encode_AlgorithmIdentifier(p, len, &(data)->signature, &l);
2585if (e) return e;
2586p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2587
2588ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2589}
2590/* serialNumber */
2591{
2592size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2593ret = 0;
2594e = encode_CertificateSerialNumber(p, len, &(data)->serialNumber, &l);
2595if (e) return e;
2596p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2597
2598ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2599}
2600/* version */
2601if((data)->version) {
2602size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2603ret = 0;
2604e = encode_Version(p, len, (data)->version, &l);
2605if (e) return e;
2606p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2607
2608e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, CONS, 0, &l);
2609if (e) return e;
2610p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2611
2612ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2613}
2614e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, &l);
2615if (e) return e;
2616p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2617
2618*size = ret;
2619return 0;
2620}
2621
2622int ASN1CALL
2623decode_TBSCertificate(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, TBSCertificate *data, size_t *size)
2624{
2625size_t ret = 0;
2626size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2627int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2628const unsigned char *begin = p;
2629
2630memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
2631{
2632size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
2633Der_type Top_type;
2634e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
2635if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
2636if(e) goto fail;
2637p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2638Top_oldlen = len;
2639if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
2640len = Top_datalen;
2641{
2642size_t version_datalen, version_oldlen;
2643Der_type version_type;
2644e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, &version_type, 0, &version_datalen, &l);
2645if (e == 0 && version_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
2646if(e) {
2647(data)->version = NULL;
2648} else {
2649(data)->version = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->version));
2650if ((data)->version == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
2651p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2652version_oldlen = len;
2653if (version_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
2654len = version_datalen;
2655e = decode_Version(p, len, (data)->version, &l);
2656if(e) goto fail;
2657p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2658len = version_oldlen - version_datalen;
2659}
2660}
2661e = decode_CertificateSerialNumber(p, len, &(data)->serialNumber, &l);
2662if(e) goto fail;
2663p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2664e = decode_AlgorithmIdentifier(p, len, &(data)->signature, &l);
2665if(e) goto fail;
2666p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2667e = decode_Name(p, len, &(data)->issuer, &l);
2668if(e) goto fail;
2669p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2670e = decode_Validity(p, len, &(data)->validity, &l);
2671if(e) goto fail;
2672p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2673e = decode_Name(p, len, &(data)->subject, &l);
2674if(e) goto fail;
2675p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2676e = decode_SubjectPublicKeyInfo(p, len, &(data)->subjectPublicKeyInfo, &l);
2677if(e) goto fail;
2678p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2679{
2680size_t issuerUniqueID_datalen, issuerUniqueID_oldlen;
2681Der_type issuerUniqueID_type;
2682e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, &issuerUniqueID_type, 1, &issuerUniqueID_datalen, &l);
2683if (e == 0 && issuerUniqueID_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
2684if(e) {
2685(data)->issuerUniqueID = NULL;
2686} else {
2687(data)->issuerUniqueID = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->issuerUniqueID));
2688if ((data)->issuerUniqueID == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
2689p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2690issuerUniqueID_oldlen = len;
2691if (issuerUniqueID_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
2692len = issuerUniqueID_datalen;
2693e = der_get_bit_string(p, len, (data)->issuerUniqueID, &l);
2694if(e) goto fail;
2695p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2696len = issuerUniqueID_oldlen - issuerUniqueID_datalen;
2697}
2698}
2699{
2700size_t subjectUniqueID_datalen, subjectUniqueID_oldlen;
2701Der_type subjectUniqueID_type;
2702e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, &subjectUniqueID_type, 2, &subjectUniqueID_datalen, &l);
2703if (e == 0 && subjectUniqueID_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
2704if(e) {
2705(data)->subjectUniqueID = NULL;
2706} else {
2707(data)->subjectUniqueID = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->subjectUniqueID));
2708if ((data)->subjectUniqueID == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
2709p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2710subjectUniqueID_oldlen = len;
2711if (subjectUniqueID_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
2712len = subjectUniqueID_datalen;
2713e = der_get_bit_string(p, len, (data)->subjectUniqueID, &l);
2714if(e) goto fail;
2715p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2716len = subjectUniqueID_oldlen - subjectUniqueID_datalen;
2717}
2718}
2719{
2720size_t extensions_datalen, extensions_oldlen;
2721Der_type extensions_type;
2722e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, &extensions_type, 3, &extensions_datalen, &l);
2723if (e == 0 && extensions_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
2724if(e) {
2725(data)->extensions = NULL;
2726} else {
2727(data)->extensions = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->extensions));
2728if ((data)->extensions == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
2729p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2730extensions_oldlen = len;
2731if (extensions_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
2732len = extensions_datalen;
2733e = decode_Extensions(p, len, (data)->extensions, &l);
2734if(e) goto fail;
2735p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2736len = extensions_oldlen - extensions_datalen;
2737}
2738}
2739len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
2740}
2741data->_save.data = calloc(1, ret);
2742if (data->_save.data == NULL) {
2743e = ENOMEM; goto fail;
2744}
2745data->_save.length = ret;
2746memcpy(data->_save.data, begin, ret);
2747if(size) *size = ret;
2748return 0;
2749fail:
2750free_TBSCertificate(data);
2751return e;
2752}
2753
2754void ASN1CALL
2755free_TBSCertificate(TBSCertificate *data)
2756{
2757der_free_octet_string(&data->_save);
2758if((data)->version) {
2759free_Version((data)->version);
2760free((data)->version);
2761(data)->version = NULL;
2762}
2763free_CertificateSerialNumber(&(data)->serialNumber);
2764free_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(data)->signature);
2765free_Name(&(data)->issuer);
2766free_Validity(&(data)->validity);
2767free_Name(&(data)->subject);
2768free_SubjectPublicKeyInfo(&(data)->subjectPublicKeyInfo);
2769if((data)->issuerUniqueID) {
2770der_free_bit_string((data)->issuerUniqueID);
2771free((data)->issuerUniqueID);
2772(data)->issuerUniqueID = NULL;
2773}
2774if((data)->subjectUniqueID) {
2775der_free_bit_string((data)->subjectUniqueID);
2776free((data)->subjectUniqueID);
2777(data)->subjectUniqueID = NULL;
2778}
2779if((data)->extensions) {
2780free_Extensions((data)->extensions);
2781free((data)->extensions);
2782(data)->extensions = NULL;
2783}
2784}

2786size_t ASN1CALL
2787length_TBSCertificate(const TBSCertificate *data)
2788{
2789size_t ret = 0;
2790if((data)->version){
2791size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
2792ret = 0;
2793ret += length_Version((data)->version);

2795ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2796}
2797{

2807ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2808}

2812ret += length_Name(&(data)->issuer);
2813ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2814}
2815{
2816size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
2817ret = 0;
2818ret += length_Validity(&(data)->validity);
2819ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2820}
2821{
2822size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
2823ret = 0;
2824ret += length_Name(&(data)->subject);
2825ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2826}
2827{

2829ret = 0;
2830ret += length_SubjectPublicKeyInfo(&(data)->subjectPublicKeyInfo);
2831ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2832}
2833if((data)->issuerUniqueID){

2857
2858int ASN1CALL
2859copy_TBSCertificate(const TBSCertificate *from, TBSCertificate *to)
2860{
2861memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
2862{ int ret;
2863ret = der_copy_octet_string(&(from)->_save, &(to)->_save);
2864if (ret) goto fail;
2865}
2866if((from)->version) {
2867(to)->version = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->version));
2868if((to)->version == NULL) goto fail;
2869if(copy_Version((from)->version, (to)->version)) goto fail;
2870}else
2871(to)->version = NULL;
2872if(copy_CertificateSerialNumber(&(from)->serialNumber, &(to)->serialNumber)) goto fail;
2873if(copy_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(from)->signature, &(to)->signature)) goto fail;
2874if(copy_Name(&(from)->issuer, &(to)->issuer)) goto fail;
2875if(copy_Validity(&(from)->validity, &(to)->validity)) goto fail;
2876if(copy_Name(&(from)->subject, &(to)->subject)) goto fail;
2877if(copy_SubjectPublicKeyInfo(&(from)->subjectPublicKeyInfo, &(to)->subjectPublicKeyInfo)) goto fail;
2878if((from)->issuerUniqueID) {
2879(to)->issuerUniqueID = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->issuerUniqueID));
2880if((to)->issuerUniqueID == NULL) goto fail;
2881if(der_copy_bit_string((from)->issuerUniqueID, (to)->issuerUniqueID)) goto fail;
2882}else
2883(to)->issuerUniqueID = NULL;
2884if((from)->subjectUniqueID) {
2885(to)->subjectUniqueID = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->subjectUniqueID));
2886if((to)->subjectUniqueID == NULL) goto fail;
2887if(der_copy_bit_string((from)->subjectUniqueID, (to)->subjectUniqueID)) goto fail;
2888}else
2889(to)->subjectUniqueID = NULL;
2890if((from)->extensions) {
2891(to)->extensions = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->extensions));
2892if((to)->extensions == NULL) goto fail;
2893if(copy_Extensions((from)->extensions, (to)->extensions)) goto fail;
2894}else
2895(to)->extensions = NULL;
2896return 0;
2897fail:
2898free_TBSCertificate(to);
2899return ENOMEM;
2900}

2902int ASN1CALL
2903encode_Certificate(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const Certificate *data, size_t *size)
2904{
2905size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
2906size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2907int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2908
2909/* signatureValue */
2910{
2911size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2912ret = 0;
2913e = der_put_bit_string(p, len, &(data)->signatureValue, &l);
2914if (e) return e;
2915p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2916
2917e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_BitString, &l);
2918if (e) return e;
2919p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2920
2921ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2922}
2923/* signatureAlgorithm */
2924{
2925size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2926ret = 0;
2927e = encode_AlgorithmIdentifier(p, len, &(data)->signatureAlgorithm, &l);
2928if (e) return e;
2929p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2930
2931ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2932}
2933/* tbsCertificate */
2934{
2935size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
2936ret = 0;
2937e = encode_TBSCertificate(p, len, &(data)->tbsCertificate, &l);
2938if (e) return e;
2939p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2940
2941ret += Top_tag_oldret;
2942}
2943e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, &l);
2944if (e) return e;
2945p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
2946
2947*size = ret;
2948return 0;
2949}
2950
2951int ASN1CALL
2952decode_Certificate(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, Certificate *data, size_t *size)
2953{
2954size_t ret = 0;
2955size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2956int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
2957
2958memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
2959{
2960size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
2961Der_type Top_type;
2962e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
2963if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
2964if(e) goto fail;
2965p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2966Top_oldlen = len;
2967if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
2968len = Top_datalen;
2969e = decode_TBSCertificate(p, len, &(data)->tbsCertificate, &l);
2970if(e) goto fail;
2971p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2972e = decode_AlgorithmIdentifier(p, len, &(data)->signatureAlgorithm, &l);
2973if(e) goto fail;
2974p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2975{
2976size_t signatureValue_datalen, signatureValue_oldlen;
2977Der_type signatureValue_type;
2978e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &signatureValue_type, UT_BitString, &signatureValue_datalen, &l);
2979if (e == 0 && signatureValue_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
2980if(e) goto fail;
2981p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2982signatureValue_oldlen = len;
2983if (signatureValue_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
2984len = signatureValue_datalen;
2985e = der_get_bit_string(p, len, &(data)->signatureValue, &l);
2986if(e) goto fail;
2987p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
2988len = signatureValue_oldlen - signatureValue_datalen;
2989}
2990len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
2991}
2992if(size) *size = ret;
2993return 0;
2994fail:
2995free_Certificate(data);
2996return e;
2997}

3071int ASN1CALL
3072decode_Certificates(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, Certificates *data, size_t *size)
3073{
3074size_t ret = 0;
3075size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
3076int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
3077
3078memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
3079{
3080size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
3081Der_type Top_type;
3082e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
3083if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
3084if(e) goto fail;
3085p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
3086Top_oldlen = len;
3087if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
3088len = Top_datalen;
3089{
3090size_t Top_Tag_origlen = len;
3091size_t Top_Tag_oldret = ret;
3092size_t Top_Tag_olen = 0;
3093void *Top_Tag_tmp;
3094ret = 0;
3095(data)->len = 0;
3096(data)->val = NULL;
3097while(ret < Top_Tag_origlen) {
3098size_t Top_Tag_nlen = Top_Tag_olen + sizeof(*((data)->val));
3099if (Top_Tag_olen > Top_Tag_nlen) { e = ASN1_OVERFLOW; goto fail; }
3100Top_Tag_olen = Top_Tag_nlen;
3101Top_Tag_tmp = realloc((data)->val, Top_Tag_olen);
3102if (Top_Tag_tmp == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
3103(data)->val = Top_Tag_tmp;
3104e = decode_Certificate(p, len, &(data)->val[(data)->len], &l);
3105if(e) goto fail;
3106p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
3107(data)->len++;
3108len = Top_Tag_origlen - ret;
3109}
3110ret += Top_Tag_oldret;
3111}
3112len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
3113}
3114if(size) *size = ret;
3115return 0;
3116fail:
3117free_Certificates(data);
3118return e;
3119}

3123{

3126(data)->len--;
3127}

3129(data)->val = NULL;
3130}

3139ret = 0;

3141size_t Top_tag_for_oldret = ret;
3142ret = 0;
3143ret += length_Certificate(&(data)->val[n_Top_tag - 1]);
3144ret += Top_tag_for_oldret;

3152int ASN1CALL
3153copy_Certificates(const Certificates *from, Certificates *to)
3154{
3155memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
3156if(((to)->val = malloc((from)->len * sizeof(*(to)->val))) == NULL && (from)->len != 0)
3157goto fail;
3158for((to)->len = 0; (to)->len < (from)->len; (to)->len++){
3159if(copy_Certificate(&(from)->val[(to)->len], &(to)->val[(to)->len])) goto fail;

3560copy_DomainParameters(const DomainParameters *from, DomainParameters *to)
3561{
3562memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
3563if(der_copy_heim_integer(&(from)->p, &(to)->p)) goto fail;
3564if(der_copy_heim_integer(&(from)->g, &(to)->g)) goto fail;

3566(to)->q = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->q));
3567if((to)->q == NULL) goto fail;
3568if(der_copy_heim_integer((from)->q, (to)->q)) goto fail;
3569}else
3570(to)->q = NULL;
3571if((from)->j) {
3572(to)->j = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->j));
3573if((to)->j == NULL) goto fail;
3574if(der_copy_heim_integer((from)->j, (to)->j)) goto fail;
3575}else
3576(to)->j = NULL;
3577if((from)->validationParms) {
3578(to)->validationParms = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->validationParms));
3579if((to)->validationParms == NULL) goto fail;
3580if(copy_ValidationParms((from)->validationParms, (to)->validationParms)) goto fail;
3581}else
3582(to)->validationParms = NULL;
3583return 0;
3584fail:
3585free_DomainParameters(to);
3586return ENOMEM;
3587}

4442copy_GeneralName(const GeneralName *from, GeneralName *to)
4443{
4444memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));

4446switch((from)->element) {
4447case choice_GeneralName_otherName:
4448if(der_copy_oid(&(&(from)->u.otherName)->type_id, &(&(to)->u.otherName)->type_id)) goto fail;
4449if(copy_heim_any(&(&(from)->u.otherName)->value, &(&(to)->u.otherName)->value)) goto fail;
4450break;
4451case choice_GeneralName_rfc822Name:
4452if(der_copy_ia5_string(&(from)->u.rfc822Name, &(to)->u.rfc822Name)) goto fail;
4453break;
4454case choice_GeneralName_dNSName:
4455if(der_copy_ia5_string(&(from)->u.dNSName, &(to)->u.dNSName)) goto fail;
4456break;
4457case choice_GeneralName_directoryName:
4458(&(to)->u.directoryName)->element = (&(from)->u.directoryName)->element;
4459switch((&(from)->u.directoryName)->element) {
4460case choice_GeneralName_directoryName_rdnSequence:
4461if(copy_RDNSequence(&(&(from)->u.directoryName)->u.rdnSequence, &(&(to)->u.directoryName)->u.rdnSequence)) goto fail;
4462break;
4463}
4464break;
4465case choice_GeneralName_uniformResourceIdentifier:
4466if(der_copy_ia5_string(&(from)->u.uniformResourceIdentifier, &(to)->u.uniformResourceIdentifier)) goto fail;
4467break;
4468case choice_GeneralName_iPAddress:
4469if(der_copy_octet_string(&(from)->u.iPAddress, &(to)->u.iPAddress)) goto fail;
4470break;
4471case choice_GeneralName_registeredID:
4472if(der_copy_oid(&(from)->u.registeredID, &(to)->u.registeredID)) goto fail;
4473break;
4474}
4475return 0;
4476fail:
4477free_GeneralName(to);
4478return ENOMEM;
4479}

4505int ASN1CALL
4506decode_GeneralNames(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, GeneralNames *data, size_t *size)
4507{
4508size_t ret = 0;
4509size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
4510int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
4511
4512memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
4513{
4514size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
4515Der_type Top_type;
4516e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
4517if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
4518if(e) goto fail;
4519p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
4520Top_oldlen = len;
4521if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
4522len = Top_datalen;
4523{
4524size_t Top_Tag_origlen = len;
4525size_t Top_Tag_oldret = ret;
4526size_t Top_Tag_olen = 0;
4527void *Top_Tag_tmp;
4528ret = 0;
4529(data)->len = 0;
4530(data)->val = NULL;
4531while(ret < Top_Tag_origlen) {
4532size_t Top_Tag_nlen = Top_Tag_olen + sizeof(*((data)->val));
4533if (Top_Tag_olen > Top_Tag_nlen) { e = ASN1_OVERFLOW; goto fail; }
4534Top_Tag_olen = Top_Tag_nlen;
4535Top_Tag_tmp = realloc((data)->val, Top_Tag_olen);
4536if (Top_Tag_tmp == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
4537(data)->val = Top_Tag_tmp;
4538e = decode_GeneralName(p, len, &(data)->val[(data)->len], &l);
4539if(e) goto fail;
4540p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
4541(data)->len++;
4542len = Top_Tag_origlen - ret;
4543}
4544ret += Top_Tag_oldret;
4545}
4546if ((data)->len > 2147483647) {
4547e = ASN1_MAX_CONSTRAINT; goto fail;
4548}
4549if ((data)->len < 1) {
4550e = ASN1_MIN_CONSTRAINT; goto fail;
4551}
4552len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
4553}
4554if(size) *size = ret;
4555return 0;
4556fail:
4557free_GeneralNames(data);
4558return e;
4559}

4607int ASN1CALL
4608add_GeneralNames(GeneralNames *data, const GeneralName *element)
4609{
4610int ret;
4611void *ptr;
4612
4613ptr = realloc(data->val,
4614 (data->len + 1) * sizeof(data->val[0]));
4615if (ptr == NULL) return ENOMEM;
4616data->val = ptr;
4617
4618ret = copy_GeneralName(element, &data->val[data->len]);
4619if (ret) return ret;
4620data->len++;
4621return 0;
4622}
4623
4624int ASN1CALL
4625remove_GeneralNames(GeneralNames *data, unsigned int element)
4626{
4627void *ptr;
4628
4629if (data->len == 0 || element >= data->len)
4630 return ASN1_OVERRUN;
4631free_GeneralName(&data->val[element]);
4632data->len--;
4633if (element < data->len)
4634 memmove(&data->val[element], &data->val[element + 1],
4635 sizeof(data->val[0]) * (data->len - element));
4636ptr = realloc(data->val, data->len * sizeof(data->val[0]));
4637if (ptr != NULL || data->len == 0) data->val = ptr;
4638return 0;
4639}

4644int ASN1CALL
4645encode_KeyUsage(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const KeyUsage *data, size_t *size)
4646{
4647size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
4648size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
4649int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
4650
4651{
4652unsigned char c = 0;
4653int rest = 0;
4654int bit_set = 0;
4655if((data)->decipherOnly) {
4656c |= 1<<7;
4657}
4658if (c != 0 || bit_set) {
4659if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
4660*p-- = c; len--; ret++;
4661if (!bit_set) {
4662rest = 0;
4663while(c) {
4664if (c & 1) break;
4665c = c >> 1;
4666rest++;
4667}
4668bit_set = 1;
4669}
4670}
4671c = 0;
4672if((data)->encipherOnly) {
4673c |= 1<<0;
4674}
4675if((data)->cRLSign) {
4676c |= 1<<1;
4677}
4678if((data)->keyCertSign) {
4679c |= 1<<2;
4680}
4681if((data)->keyAgreement) {
4682c |= 1<<3;
4683}
4684if((data)->dataEncipherment) {
4685c |= 1<<4;
4686}
4687if((data)->keyEncipherment) {
4688c |= 1<<5;
4689}
4690if((data)->nonRepudiation) {
4691c |= 1<<6;
4692}
4693if((data)->digitalSignature) {
4694c |= 1<<7;
4695}
4696if (c != 0 || bit_set) {
4697if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
4698*p-- = c; len--; ret++;
4699if (!bit_set) {
4700rest = 0;
4701if(c) {
4702while(c) {
4703if (c & 1) break;
4704c = c >> 1;
4705rest++;
4706}
4707}
4708}
4709}
4710if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
4711*p-- = rest;
4712len -= 1;
4713ret += 1;
4714}
4715
4716e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_BitString, &l);
4717if (e) return e;
4718p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
4719
4720*size = ret;
4721return 0;
4722}

4724int ASN1CALL
4725decode_KeyUsage(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, KeyUsage *data, size_t *size)
4726{
4727size_t ret = 0;
4728size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
4729int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
4730
4731memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
4732{
4733size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
4734Der_type Top_type;
4735e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_BitString, &Top_datalen, &l);
4736if (e == 0 && Top_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
4737if(e) goto fail;
4738p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
4739Top_oldlen = len;
4740if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
4741len = Top_datalen;
4742if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERRUN;
4743p++; len--; ret++;
4744do {
4745if (len < 1) break;
4746(data)->digitalSignature = (*p >> 7) & 1;
4747(data)->nonRepudiation = (*p >> 6) & 1;
4748(data)->keyEncipherment = (*p >> 5) & 1;
4749(data)->dataEncipherment = (*p >> 4) & 1;
4750(data)->keyAgreement = (*p >> 3) & 1;
4751(data)->keyCertSign = (*p >> 2) & 1;
4752(data)->cRLSign = (*p >> 1) & 1;
4753(data)->encipherOnly = (*p >> 0) & 1;
4754p++; len--; ret++;
4755if (len < 1) break;
4756(data)->decipherOnly = (*p >> 7) & 1;
4757} while(0);
4758p += len; ret += len;
4759len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
4760}
4761if(size) *size = ret;
4762return 0;
4763fail:
4764free_KeyUsage(data);
4765return e;
4766}

4771}

4773size_t ASN1CALL
4774length_KeyUsage(const KeyUsage *data)
4775{
4776size_t ret = 0;
4777do {
4778if((data)->decipherOnly) { ret += 2; break; }
4779if((data)->encipherOnly) { ret += 1; break; }
4780if((data)->cRLSign) { ret += 1; break; }
4781if((data)->keyCertSign) { ret += 1; break; }
4782if((data)->keyAgreement) { ret += 1; break; }
4783if((data)->dataEncipherment) { ret += 1; break; }
4784if((data)->keyEncipherment) { ret += 1; break; }
4785if((data)->nonRepudiation) { ret += 1; break; }
4786if((data)->digitalSignature) { ret += 1; break; }
4787} while(0);
4788ret += 1;
4789ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
4790return ret;
4791}

4801unsigned KeyUsage2int(KeyUsage f)
4802{
4803unsigned r = 0;
4804if(f.digitalSignature) r |= (1U << 0);
4805if(f.nonRepudiation) r |= (1U << 1);
4806if(f.keyEncipherment) r |= (1U << 2);
4807if(f.dataEncipherment) r |= (1U << 3);
4808if(f.keyAgreement) r |= (1U << 4);
4809if(f.keyCertSign) r |= (1U << 5);
4810if(f.cRLSign) r |= (1U << 6);
4811if(f.encipherOnly) r |= (1U << 7);
4812if(f.decipherOnly) r |= (1U << 8);
4813return r;
4814}
4815
4816KeyUsage int2KeyUsage(unsigned n)
4817{
4818 KeyUsage flags;
4819
4820 memset(&flags, 0, sizeof(flags));
4821
4822 flags.digitalSignature = (n >> 0) & 1;
4823 flags.nonRepudiation = (n >> 1) & 1;
4824 flags.keyEncipherment = (n >> 2) & 1;
4825 flags.dataEncipherment = (n >> 3) & 1;
4826 flags.keyAgreement = (n >> 4) & 1;
4827 flags.keyCertSign = (n >> 5) & 1;
4828 flags.cRLSign = (n >> 6) & 1;
4829 flags.encipherOnly = (n >> 7) & 1;
4830 flags.decipherOnly = (n >> 8) & 1;
4831 return flags;
4832}

5032e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, &authorityCertIssuer_type, 1, &authorityCertIssuer_datalen, &l);
5033if (e == 0 && authorityCertIssuer_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }

5039p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
5040authorityCertIssuer_oldlen = len;

5042len = authorityCertIssuer_datalen;
5043{
5044size_t authorityCertIssuer_Tag_origlen = len;
5045size_t authorityCertIssuer_Tag_oldret = ret;
5046size_t authorityCertIssuer_Tag_olen = 0;

5179if(copy_GeneralName(&((from)->authorityCertIssuer)->val[((to)->authorityCertIssuer)->len], &((to)->authorityCertIssuer)->val[((to)->authorityCertIssuer)->len])) goto fail;
5180}
5181}else
5182(to)->authorityCertIssuer = NULL;

6255int ASN1CALL
6256encode_DistributionPointReasonFlags(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const DistributionPointReasonFlags *data, size_t *size)
6257{
6258size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
6259size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
6260int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
6261
6262{
6263unsigned char c = 0;
6264int rest = 0;
6265int bit_set = 0;
6266if((data)->aACompromise) {
6267c |= 1<<7;
6268}
6269if (c != 0 || bit_set) {
6270if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
6271*p-- = c; len--; ret++;
6272if (!bit_set) {
6273rest = 0;
6274while(c) {
6275if (c & 1) break;
6276c = c >> 1;
6277rest++;
6278}
6279bit_set = 1;
6280}
6281}
6282c = 0;
6283if((data)->privilegeWithdrawn) {
6284c |= 1<<0;
6285}
6286if((data)->certificateHold) {
6287c |= 1<<1;
6288}
6289if((data)->cessationOfOperation) {
6290c |= 1<<2;
6291}
6292if((data)->superseded) {
6293c |= 1<<3;
6294}
6295if((data)->affiliationChanged) {
6296c |= 1<<4;
6297}
6298if((data)->cACompromise) {
6299c |= 1<<5;
6300}
6301if((data)->keyCompromise) {
6302c |= 1<<6;
6303}
6304if((data)->unused) {
6305c |= 1<<7;
6306}
6307if (c != 0 || bit_set) {
6308if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
6309*p-- = c; len--; ret++;
6310if (!bit_set) {
6311rest = 0;
6312if(c) {
6313while(c) {
6314if (c & 1) break;
6315c = c >> 1;
6316rest++;
6317}
6318}
6319}
6320}
6321if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
6322*p-- = rest;
6323len -= 1;
6324ret += 1;
6325}
6326
6327e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_BitString, &l);
6328if (e) return e;
6329p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
6330
6331*size = ret;
6332return 0;
6333}

6336decode_DistributionPointReasonFlags(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, DistributionPointReasonFlags *data, size_t *size)
6337{
6338size_t ret = 0;
6339size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
6340int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
6341
6342memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
6343{
6344size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
6345Der_type Top_type;
6346e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_BitString, &Top_datalen, &l);

6350Top_oldlen = len;

6352len = Top_datalen;
6353if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERRUN;
6354p++; len--; ret++;
6355do {
6356if (len < 1) break;
6357(data)->unused = (*p >> 7) & 1;
6358(data)->keyCompromise = (*p >> 6) & 1;
6359(data)->cACompromise = (*p >> 5) & 1;
6360(data)->affiliationChanged = (*p >> 4) & 1;
6361(data)->superseded = (*p >> 3) & 1;
6362(data)->cessationOfOperation = (*p >> 2) & 1;
6363(data)->certificateHold = (*p >> 1) & 1;
6364(data)->privilegeWithdrawn = (*p >> 0) & 1;
6365p++; len--; ret++;
6366if (len < 1) break;
6367(data)->aACompromise = (*p >> 7) & 1;
6368} while(0);
6369p += len; ret += len;
6370len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
6371}
6372if(size) *size = ret;
6373return 0;
6374fail:

6412unsigned DistributionPointReasonFlags2int(DistributionPointReasonFlags f)
6413{
6414unsigned r = 0;
6415if(f.unused) r |= (1U << 0);
6416if(f.keyCompromise) r |= (1U << 1);
6417if(f.cACompromise) r |= (1U << 2);
6418if(f.affiliationChanged) r |= (1U << 3);
6419if(f.superseded) r |= (1U << 4);
6420if(f.cessationOfOperation) r |= (1U << 5);
6421if(f.certificateHold) r |= (1U << 6);
6422if(f.privilegeWithdrawn) r |= (1U << 7);
6423if(f.aACompromise) r |= (1U << 8);
6424return r;
6425}

6427DistributionPointReasonFlags int2DistributionPointReasonFlags(unsigned n)
6428{
6429 DistributionPointReasonFlags flags;
6430
6431 memset(&flags, 0, sizeof(flags));
6432
6433 flags.unused = (n >> 0) & 1;
6434 flags.keyCompromise = (n >> 1) & 1;
6435 flags.cACompromise = (n >> 2) & 1;
6436 flags.affiliationChanged = (n >> 3) & 1;
6437 flags.superseded = (n >> 4) & 1;
6438 flags.cessationOfOperation = (n >> 5) & 1;
6439 flags.certificateHold = (n >> 6) & 1;
6440 flags.privilegeWithdrawn = (n >> 7) & 1;
6441 flags.aACompromise = (n >> 8) & 1;
6442 return flags;
6443}

6667int ASN1CALL

6669{
6670size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
6671size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;

6674/* cRLIssuer */

6679if (e) return e;
6680p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
6681
6682e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, CONS, 2, &l);
6683if (e) return e;
6684p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
6685
6686ret += Top_tag_oldret;
6687}
6688/* reasons */
6689if((data)->reasons) {
6690size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
6691ret = 0;
6692e = encode_heim_any(p, len, (data)->reasons, &l);
6693if (e) return e;
6694p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
6695
6696e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, CONS, 1, &l);
6697if (e) return e;
6698p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
6699
6700ret += Top_tag_oldret;
6701}
6702/* distributionPoint */
6703if((data)->distributionPoint) {
6704size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
6705ret = 0;
6706e = encode_heim_any(p, len, (data)->distributionPoint, &l);
6707if (e) return e;
6708p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
6709
6710e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, CONS, 0, &l);
6711if (e) return e;
6712p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
6713
6714ret += Top_tag_oldret;
6715}
6716e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, &l);
6717if (e) return e;
6718p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
6719
6720*size = ret;
6721return 0;
6722}

6724int ASN1CALL
6725decode_DistributionPoint(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, DistributionPoint *data, size_t *size)
6726{
6727size_t ret = 0;
6728size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
6729int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
6730
6731memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
6732{
6733size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
6734Der_type Top_type;
6735e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
6736if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
6737if(e) goto fail;
6738p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
6739Top_oldlen = len;
6740if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
6741len = Top_datalen;
6742{
6743size_t distributionPoint_datalen, distributionPoint_oldlen;
6744Der_type distributionPoint_type;
6745e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, &distributionPoint_type, 0, &distributionPoint_datalen, &l);
6746if (e == 0 && distributionPoint_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
6747if(e) {
6748(data)->distributionPoint = NULL;
6749} else {
6750(data)->distributionPoint = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->distributionPoint));
6751if ((data)->distributionPoint == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
6752p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
6753distributionPoint_oldlen = len;
6754if (distributionPoint_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
6755len = distributionPoint_datalen;
6756e = decode_heim_any(p, len, (data)->distributionPoint, &l);
6757if(e) goto fail;
6758p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
6759len = distributionPoint_oldlen - distributionPoint_datalen;
6760}
6761}
6762{
6763size_t reasons_datalen, reasons_oldlen;
6764Der_type reasons_type;
6765e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, &reasons_type, 1, &reasons_datalen, &l);
6766if (e == 0 && reasons_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
6767if(e) {
6768(data)->reasons = NULL;
6769} else {
6770(data)->reasons = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->reasons));
6771if ((data)->reasons == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
6772p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
6773reasons_oldlen = len;
6774if (reasons_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
6775len = reasons_datalen;
6776e = decode_heim_any(p, len, (data)->reasons, &l);
6777if(e) goto fail;
6778p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
6779len = reasons_oldlen - reasons_datalen;
6780}
6781}
6782{
6783size_t cRLIssuer_datalen, cRLIssuer_oldlen;
6784Der_type cRLIssuer_type;
6785e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, &cRLIssuer_type, 2, &cRLIssuer_datalen, &l);
6786if (e == 0 && cRLIssuer_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
6787if(e) {
6788(data)->cRLIssuer = NULL;
6789} else {
6790(data)->cRLIssuer = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->cRLIssuer));
6791if ((data)->cRLIssuer == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
6792p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
6793cRLIssuer_oldlen = len;
6794if (cRLIssuer_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
6795len = cRLIssuer_datalen;
6796e = decode_heim_any(p, len, (data)->cRLIssuer, &l);
6797if(e) goto fail;
6798p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
6799len = cRLIssuer_oldlen - cRLIssuer_datalen;
6800}
6801}
6802len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
6803}
6804if(size) *size = ret;
6805return 0;
6806fail:
6807free_DistributionPoint(data);
6808return e;
6809}

6811void ASN1CALL
6812free_DistributionPoint(DistributionPoint *data)
6813{
6814if((data)->distributionPoint) {
6815free_heim_any((data)->distributionPoint);
6816free((data)->distributionPoint);
6817(data)->distributionPoint = NULL;
6818}
6819if((data)->reasons) {
6820free_heim_any((data)->reasons);
6821free((data)->reasons);
6822(data)->reasons = NULL;
6823}
6824if((data)->cRLIssuer) {
6825free_heim_any((data)->cRLIssuer);
6826free((data)->cRLIssuer);
6827(data)->cRLIssuer = NULL;
6828}
6829}

6831size_t ASN1CALL
6832length_DistributionPoint(const DistributionPoint *data)
6833{
6834size_t ret = 0;
6835if((data)->distributionPoint){
6836size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
6837ret = 0;
6838ret += length_heim_any((data)->distributionPoint);
6839ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
6840ret += Top_tag_oldret;
6841}
6842if((data)->reasons){
6843size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
6844ret = 0;
6845ret += length_heim_any((data)->reasons);
6846ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
6847ret += Top_tag_oldret;
6848}
6849if((data)->cRLIssuer){
6850size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
6851ret = 0;
6852ret += length_heim_any((data)->cRLIssuer);
6853ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
6854ret += Top_tag_oldret;
6855}
6856ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
6857return ret;
6858}

6860int ASN1CALL
6861copy_DistributionPoint(const DistributionPoint *from, DistributionPoint *to)
6862{
6863memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
6864if((from)->distributionPoint) {
6865(to)->distributionPoint = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->distributionPoint));
6866if((to)->distributionPoint == NULL) goto fail;
6867if(copy_heim_any((from)->distributionPoint, (to)->distributionPoint)) goto fail;
6868}else
6869(to)->distributionPoint = NULL;
6870if((from)->reasons) {
6871(to)->reasons = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->reasons));
6872if((to)->reasons == NULL) goto fail;
6873if(copy_heim_any((from)->reasons, (to)->reasons)) goto fail;
6874}else
6875(to)->reasons = NULL;
6876if((from)->cRLIssuer) {
6877(to)->cRLIssuer = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->cRLIssuer));
6878if((to)->cRLIssuer == NULL) goto fail;
6879if(copy_heim_any((from)->cRLIssuer, (to)->cRLIssuer)) goto fail;
6880}else
6881(to)->cRLIssuer = NULL;
6882return 0;
6883fail:
6884free_DistributionPoint(to);
6885return ENOMEM;
6886}

6912int ASN1CALL
6913decode_CRLDistributionPoints(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, CRLDistributionPoints *data, size_t *size)
6914{
6915size_t ret = 0;
6916size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
6917int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
6918
6919memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
6920{
6921size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
6922Der_type Top_type;
6923e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
6924if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
6925if(e) goto fail;
6926p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
6927Top_oldlen = len;
6928if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
6929len = Top_datalen;
6930{
6931size_t Top_Tag_origlen = len;
6932size_t Top_Tag_oldret = ret;
6933size_t Top_Tag_olen = 0;
6934void *Top_Tag_tmp;
6935ret = 0;
6936(data)->len = 0;
6937(data)->val = NULL;
6938while(ret < Top_Tag_origlen) {
6939size_t Top_Tag_nlen = Top_Tag_olen + sizeof(*((data)->val));
6940if (Top_Tag_olen > Top_Tag_nlen) { e = ASN1_OVERFLOW; goto fail; }
6941Top_Tag_olen = Top_Tag_nlen;
6942Top_Tag_tmp = realloc((data)->val, Top_Tag_olen);
6943if (Top_Tag_tmp == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
6944(data)->val = Top_Tag_tmp;
6945e = decode_DistributionPoint(p, len, &(data)->val[(data)->len], &l);
6946if(e) goto fail;
6947p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
6948(data)->len++;
6949len = Top_Tag_origlen - ret;
6950}
6951ret += Top_Tag_oldret;
6952}
6953if ((data)->len > 2147483647) {
6954e = ASN1_MAX_CONSTRAINT; goto fail;
6955}
6956if ((data)->len < 1) {
6957e = ASN1_MIN_CONSTRAINT; goto fail;
6958}
6959len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
6960}
6961if(size) *size = ret;
6962return 0;
6963fail:
6964free_CRLDistributionPoints(data);
6965return e;
6966}

6968void ASN1CALL
6969free_CRLDistributionPoints(CRLDistributionPoints *data)
6970{
6971while((data)->len){
6972free_DistributionPoint(&(data)->val[(data)->len-1]);
6973(data)->len--;
6974}
6975free((data)->val);
6976(data)->val = NULL;
6977}

6979size_t ASN1CALL
6980length_CRLDistributionPoints(const CRLDistributionPoints *data)
6981{
6982size_t ret = 0;
6983{
6984size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
6985unsigned int n_Top_tag;
6986ret = 0;
6987for(n_Top_tag = (data)->len; n_Top_tag > 0; --n_Top_tag){
6988size_t Top_tag_for_oldret = ret;
6989ret = 0;
6990ret += length_DistributionPoint(&(data)->val[n_Top_tag - 1]);
6991ret += Top_tag_for_oldret;
6992}
6993ret += Top_tag_oldret;
6994}
6995ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
6996return ret;

6999int ASN1CALL
7000copy_CRLDistributionPoints(const CRLDistributionPoints *from, CRLDistributionPoints *to)
7001{
7002memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
7003if(((to)->val = malloc((from)->len * sizeof(*(to)->val))) == NULL && (from)->len != 0)
7004goto fail;
7005for((to)->len = 0; (to)->len < (from)->len; (to)->len++){
7006if(copy_DistributionPoint(&(from)->val[(to)->len], &(to)->val[(to)->len])) goto fail;
7007}
7008return 0;
7009fail:
7010free_CRLDistributionPoints(to);
7011return ENOMEM;
7012}
7013
7014int ASN1CALL
7015add_CRLDistributionPoints(CRLDistributionPoints *data, const DistributionPoint *element)
7016{
7017int ret;
7018void *ptr;
7019
7020ptr = realloc(data->val,
7021 (data->len + 1) * sizeof(data->val[0]));
7022if (ptr == NULL) return ENOMEM;
7023data->val = ptr;
7024
7025ret = copy_DistributionPoint(element, &data->val[data->len]);
7026if (ret) return ret;
7027data->len++;
7028return 0;
7029}
7030
7031int ASN1CALL
7032remove_CRLDistributionPoints(CRLDistributionPoints *data, unsigned int element)
7033{
7034void *ptr;
7035
7036if (data->len == 0 || element >= data->len)
7037 return ASN1_OVERRUN;
7038free_DistributionPoint(&data->val[element]);
7039data->len--;
7040if (element < data->len)
7041 memmove(&data->val[element], &data->val[element + 1],
7042 sizeof(data->val[0]) * (data->len - element));
7043ptr = realloc(data->val, data->len * sizeof(data->val[0]));
7044if (ptr != NULL || data->len == 0) data->val = ptr;
7045return 0;
7046}

7831e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &modulus_type, UT_Integer, &modulus_datalen, &l);
7832if (e == 0 && modulus_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
7833if(e) goto fail;
7834p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
7835modulus_oldlen = len;
7836if (modulus_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
7837len = modulus_datalen;
7838e = der_get_heim_integer(p, len, &(data)->modulus, &l);
7839if(e) goto fail;
7840p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
7841len = modulus_oldlen - modulus_datalen;
7842}
7843{
7844size_t publicExponent_datalen, publicExponent_oldlen;
7845Der_type publicExponent_type;
7846e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &publicExponent_type, UT_Integer, &publicExponent_datalen, &l);
7847if (e == 0 && publicExponent_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
7848if(e) goto fail;
7849p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
7850publicExponent_oldlen = len;
7851if (publicExponent_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
7852len = publicExponent_datalen;
7853e = der_get_heim_integer(p, len, &(data)->publicExponent, &l);
7854if(e) goto fail;
7855p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
7856len = publicExponent_oldlen - publicExponent_datalen;
7857}
7858len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
7859}
7860if(size) *size = ret;
7861return 0;
7862fail:
7863free_RSAPublicKey(data);
7864return e;
7865}

8294
8295int ASN1CALL
8296copy_RSAPrivateKey(const RSAPrivateKey *from, RSAPrivateKey *to)
8297{
8298memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
8299*(&(to)->version) = *(&(from)->version);
8300if(der_copy_heim_integer(&(from)->modulus, &(to)->modulus)) goto fail;
8301if(der_copy_heim_integer(&(from)->publicExponent, &(to)->publicExponent)) goto fail;
8302if(der_copy_heim_integer(&(from)->privateExponent, &(to)->privateExponent)) goto fail;
8303if(der_copy_heim_integer(&(from)->prime1, &(to)->prime1)) goto fail;
8304if(der_copy_heim_integer(&(from)->prime2, &(to)->prime2)) goto fail;
8305if(der_copy_heim_integer(&(from)->exponent1, &(to)->exponent1)) goto fail;
8306if(der_copy_heim_integer(&(from)->exponent2, &(to)->exponent2)) goto fail;
8307if(der_copy_heim_integer(&(from)->coefficient, &(to)->coefficient)) goto fail;
8308return 0;
8309fail:
8310free_RSAPrivateKey(to);
8311return ENOMEM;
8312}

8314int ASN1CALL
8315encode_DigestInfo(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const DigestInfo *data, size_t *size)
8316{
8317size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
8318size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
8319int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
8320
8321/* digest */
8322{
8323size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8324ret = 0;
8325e = der_put_octet_string(p, len, &(data)->digest, &l);
8326if (e) return e;
8327p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8328
8329e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_OctetString, &l);
8330if (e) return e;
8331p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8332
8333ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8334}
8335/* digestAlgorithm */
8336{
8337size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8338ret = 0;
8339e = encode_AlgorithmIdentifier(p, len, &(data)->digestAlgorithm, &l);
8340if (e) return e;
8341p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8342
8343ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8344}
8345e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, &l);
8346if (e) return e;
8347p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8348
8349*size = ret;
8350return 0;
8351}

8362size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
8363Der_type Top_type;
8364e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
8365if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
8366if(e) goto fail;
8367p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8368Top_oldlen = len;
8369if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
8370len = Top_datalen;
8371e = decode_AlgorithmIdentifier(p, len, &(data)->digestAlgorithm, &l);
8372if(e) goto fail;
8373p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8374{
8375size_t digest_datalen, digest_oldlen;
8376Der_type digest_type;
8377e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &digest_type, UT_OctetString, &digest_datalen, &l);
8378if (e == 0 && digest_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
8379if(e) goto fail;
8380p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8381digest_oldlen = len;
8382if (digest_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
8383len = digest_datalen;
8384e = der_get_octet_string(p, len, &(data)->digest, &l);
8385if(e) goto fail;
8386p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8387len = digest_oldlen - digest_datalen;
8388}
8389len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
8390}
8391if(size) *size = ret;
8392return 0;
8393fail:
8394free_DigestInfo(data);
8395return e;
8396}
8397
8398void ASN1CALL
8399free_DigestInfo(DigestInfo *data)
8400{
8401free_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(data)->digestAlgorithm);
8402der_free_octet_string(&(data)->digest);
8403}
8404
8405size_t ASN1CALL
8406length_DigestInfo(const DigestInfo *data)
8407{
8408size_t ret = 0;
8409{
8410size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
8411ret = 0;
8412ret += length_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(data)->digestAlgorithm);
8413ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8414}
8415{
8416size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
8417ret = 0;
8418ret += der_length_octet_string(&(data)->digest);
8419ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
8420ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8421}
8422ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
8423return ret;
8424}
8425
8426int ASN1CALL
8427copy_DigestInfo(const DigestInfo *from, DigestInfo *to)
8428{
8429memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
8430if(copy_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(from)->digestAlgorithm, &(to)->digestAlgorithm)) goto fail;
8431if(der_copy_octet_string(&(from)->digest, &(to)->digest)) goto fail;
8432return 0;
8433fail:
8434free_DigestInfo(to);
8435return ENOMEM;
8436}
