8438int ASN1CALL
8439encode_TBSCRLCertList(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const TBSCRLCertList *data, size_t *size)
8440{
8441size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
8442size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
8443int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
8444
8445/* crlExtensions */
8446if((data)->crlExtensions) {
8447size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8448ret = 0;
8449e = encode_Extensions(p, len, (data)->crlExtensions, &l);
8450if (e) return e;
8451p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8452
8453e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, CONS, 0, &l);
8454if (e) return e;
8455p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8456
8457ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8458}
8459/* revokedCertificates */
8460if((data)->revokedCertificates) {
8461size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8462ret = 0;
8463for(i = (int)((data)->revokedCertificates)->len - 1; i >= 0; --i) {
8464size_t revokedCertificates_tag_for_oldret = ret;
8465ret = 0;
8466/* crlEntryExtensions */
8467if((&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[i])->crlEntryExtensions) {
8468size_t revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8469ret = 0;
8470e = encode_Extensions(p, len, (&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[i])->crlEntryExtensions, &l);
8471if (e) return e;
8472p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8473
8474ret += revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret;
8475}
8476/* revocationDate */
8477{
8478size_t revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8479ret = 0;
8480e = encode_Time(p, len, &(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[i])->revocationDate, &l);
8481if (e) return e;
8482p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8483
8484ret += revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret;
8485}
8486/* userCertificate */
8487{
8488size_t revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8489ret = 0;
8490e = encode_CertificateSerialNumber(p, len, &(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[i])->userCertificate, &l);
8491if (e) return e;
8492p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8493
8494ret += revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret;
8495}
8496e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, &l);
8497if (e) return e;
8498p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8499
8500ret += revokedCertificates_tag_for_oldret;
8501}
8502e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, &l);
8503if (e) return e;
8504p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8505
8506ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8507}
8508/* nextUpdate */
8509if((data)->nextUpdate) {
8510size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8511ret = 0;
8512e = encode_Time(p, len, (data)->nextUpdate, &l);
8513if (e) return e;
8514p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8515
8516ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8517}
8518/* thisUpdate */
8519{
8520size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8521ret = 0;
8522e = encode_Time(p, len, &(data)->thisUpdate, &l);
8523if (e) return e;
8524p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8525
8526ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8527}
8528/* issuer */
8529{
8530size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8531ret = 0;
8532e = encode_Name(p, len, &(data)->issuer, &l);
8533if (e) return e;
8534p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8535
8536ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8537}
8538/* signature */
8539{
8540size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8541ret = 0;
8542e = encode_AlgorithmIdentifier(p, len, &(data)->signature, &l);
8543if (e) return e;
8544p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8545
8546ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8547}
8548/* version */
8549if((data)->version) {
8550size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
8551ret = 0;
8552e = encode_Version(p, len, (data)->version, &l);
8553if (e) return e;
8554p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8555
8556ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8557}
8558e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, &l);
8559if (e) return e;
8560p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
8561
8562*size = ret;
8563return 0;
8564}

8566int ASN1CALL
8567decode_TBSCRLCertList(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, TBSCRLCertList *data, size_t *size)
8568{
8569size_t ret = 0;
8570size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
8571int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
8572const unsigned char *begin = p;
8573
8574memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
8575{
8576size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
8577Der_type Top_type;
8578e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
8579if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
8580if(e) goto fail;
8581p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8582Top_oldlen = len;
8583if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
8584len = Top_datalen;
8585(data)->version = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->version));
8586if ((data)->version == NULL) goto fail;
8587e = decode_Version(p, len, (data)->version, &l);
8588if(e) {
8589free((data)->version);
8590(data)->version = NULL;
8591} else {
8592p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8593}
8594e = decode_AlgorithmIdentifier(p, len, &(data)->signature, &l);
8595if(e) goto fail;
8596p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8597e = decode_Name(p, len, &(data)->issuer, &l);
8598if(e) goto fail;
8599p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8600e = decode_Time(p, len, &(data)->thisUpdate, &l);
8601if(e) goto fail;
8602p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8603(data)->nextUpdate = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->nextUpdate));
8604if ((data)->nextUpdate == NULL) goto fail;
8605e = decode_Time(p, len, (data)->nextUpdate, &l);
8606if(e) {
8607free((data)->nextUpdate);
8608(data)->nextUpdate = NULL;
8609} else {
8610p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8611}
8612{
8613size_t revokedCertificates_datalen, revokedCertificates_oldlen;
8614Der_type revokedCertificates_type;
8615e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &revokedCertificates_type, UT_Sequence, &revokedCertificates_datalen, &l);
8616if (e == 0 && revokedCertificates_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
8617if(e) {
8618(data)->revokedCertificates = NULL;
8619} else {
8620(data)->revokedCertificates = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->revokedCertificates));
8621if ((data)->revokedCertificates == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
8622p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8623revokedCertificates_oldlen = len;
8624if (revokedCertificates_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
8625len = revokedCertificates_datalen;
8626{
8627size_t revokedCertificates_Tag_origlen = len;
8628size_t revokedCertificates_Tag_oldret = ret;
8629size_t revokedCertificates_Tag_olen = 0;
8630void *revokedCertificates_Tag_tmp;
8631ret = 0;
8632((data)->revokedCertificates)->len = 0;
8633((data)->revokedCertificates)->val = NULL;
8634while(ret < revokedCertificates_Tag_origlen) {
8635size_t revokedCertificates_Tag_nlen = revokedCertificates_Tag_olen + sizeof(*(((data)->revokedCertificates)->val));
8636if (revokedCertificates_Tag_olen > revokedCertificates_Tag_nlen) { e = ASN1_OVERFLOW; goto fail; }
8637revokedCertificates_Tag_olen = revokedCertificates_Tag_nlen;
8638revokedCertificates_Tag_tmp = realloc(((data)->revokedCertificates)->val, revokedCertificates_Tag_olen);
8639if (revokedCertificates_Tag_tmp == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
8640((data)->revokedCertificates)->val = revokedCertificates_Tag_tmp;
8641{
8642size_t revokedCertificates_Tag_s_of_datalen, revokedCertificates_Tag_s_of_oldlen;
8643Der_type revokedCertificates_Tag_s_of_type;
8644e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &revokedCertificates_Tag_s_of_type, UT_Sequence, &revokedCertificates_Tag_s_of_datalen, &l);
8645if (e == 0 && revokedCertificates_Tag_s_of_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
8646if(e) goto fail;
8647p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8648revokedCertificates_Tag_s_of_oldlen = len;
8649if (revokedCertificates_Tag_s_of_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
8650len = revokedCertificates_Tag_s_of_datalen;
8651e = decode_CertificateSerialNumber(p, len, &(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len])->userCertificate, &l);
8652if(e) goto fail;
8653p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8654e = decode_Time(p, len, &(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len])->revocationDate, &l);
8655if(e) goto fail;
8656p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8657(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions = calloc(1, sizeof(*(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions));
8658if ((&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions == NULL) goto fail;
8659e = decode_Extensions(p, len, (&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions, &l);
8660if(e) {
8661free((&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions);
8662(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions = NULL;
8663} else {
8664p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8665}
8666len = revokedCertificates_Tag_s_of_oldlen - revokedCertificates_Tag_s_of_datalen;
8667}
8668((data)->revokedCertificates)->len++;
8669len = revokedCertificates_Tag_origlen - ret;
8670}
8671ret += revokedCertificates_Tag_oldret;
8672}
8673len = revokedCertificates_oldlen - revokedCertificates_datalen;
8674}
8675}
8676{
8677size_t crlExtensions_datalen, crlExtensions_oldlen;
8678Der_type crlExtensions_type;
8679e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_CONTEXT, &crlExtensions_type, 0, &crlExtensions_datalen, &l);
8680if (e == 0 && crlExtensions_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
8681if(e) {
8682(data)->crlExtensions = NULL;
8683} else {
8684(data)->crlExtensions = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->crlExtensions));
8685if ((data)->crlExtensions == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
8686p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8687crlExtensions_oldlen = len;
8688if (crlExtensions_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
8689len = crlExtensions_datalen;
8690e = decode_Extensions(p, len, (data)->crlExtensions, &l);
8691if(e) goto fail;
8692p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
8693len = crlExtensions_oldlen - crlExtensions_datalen;
8694}
8695}
8696len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
8697}
8698data->_save.data = calloc(1, ret);
8699if (data->_save.data == NULL) {
8700e = ENOMEM; goto fail;
8701}
8702data->_save.length = ret;
8703memcpy(data->_save.data, begin, ret);
8704if(size) *size = ret;
8705return 0;
8706fail:
8707free_TBSCRLCertList(data);
8708return e;
8709}
8710
8711void ASN1CALL
8712free_TBSCRLCertList(TBSCRLCertList *data)
8713{
8714der_free_octet_string(&data->_save);
8715if((data)->version) {
8716free_Version((data)->version);
8717free((data)->version);
8718(data)->version = NULL;
8719}
8720free_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(data)->signature);
8721free_Name(&(data)->issuer);
8722free_Time(&(data)->thisUpdate);
8723if((data)->nextUpdate) {
8724free_Time((data)->nextUpdate);
8725free((data)->nextUpdate);
8726(data)->nextUpdate = NULL;
8727}
8728if((data)->revokedCertificates) {
8729while(((data)->revokedCertificates)->len){
8730free_CertificateSerialNumber(&(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len-1])->userCertificate);
8731free_Time(&(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len-1])->revocationDate);
8732if((&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len-1])->crlEntryExtensions) {
8733free_Extensions((&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len-1])->crlEntryExtensions);
8734free((&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len-1])->crlEntryExtensions);
8735(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[((data)->revokedCertificates)->len-1])->crlEntryExtensions = NULL;
8736}
8737((data)->revokedCertificates)->len--;
8738}
8739free(((data)->revokedCertificates)->val);
8740((data)->revokedCertificates)->val = NULL;
8741free((data)->revokedCertificates);
8742(data)->revokedCertificates = NULL;
8743}
8744if((data)->crlExtensions) {
8745free_Extensions((data)->crlExtensions);
8746free((data)->crlExtensions);
8747(data)->crlExtensions = NULL;
8748}
8749}

8751size_t ASN1CALL
8752length_TBSCRLCertList(const TBSCRLCertList *data)
8753{
8754size_t ret = 0;
8755if((data)->version){
8756size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
8757ret = 0;
8758ret += length_Version((data)->version);
8759ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8760}
8761{
8762size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
8763ret = 0;
8764ret += length_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(data)->signature);
8765ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8766}
8767{
8768size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
8769ret = 0;
8770ret += length_Name(&(data)->issuer);
8771ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8772}
8773{
8774size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
8775ret = 0;
8776ret += length_Time(&(data)->thisUpdate);
8777ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8778}
8779if((data)->nextUpdate){
8780size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
8781ret = 0;
8782ret += length_Time((data)->nextUpdate);
8783ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8784}
8785if((data)->revokedCertificates){
8786size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
8787ret = 0;
8788{
8789size_t revokedCertificates_tag_oldret = ret;
8790unsigned int n_revokedCertificates_tag;
8791ret = 0;
8792for(n_revokedCertificates_tag = ((data)->revokedCertificates)->len; n_revokedCertificates_tag > 0; --n_revokedCertificates_tag){
8793size_t revokedCertificates_tag_for_oldret = ret;
8794ret = 0;
8795{
8796size_t revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret = ret;
8797ret = 0;
8798ret += length_CertificateSerialNumber(&(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[n_revokedCertificates_tag - 1])->userCertificate);
8799ret += revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret;
8800}
8801{
8802size_t revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret = ret;
8803ret = 0;
8804ret += length_Time(&(&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[n_revokedCertificates_tag - 1])->revocationDate);
8805ret += revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret;
8806}
8807if((&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[n_revokedCertificates_tag - 1])->crlEntryExtensions){
8808size_t revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret = ret;
8809ret = 0;
8810ret += length_Extensions((&((data)->revokedCertificates)->val[n_revokedCertificates_tag - 1])->crlEntryExtensions);
8811ret += revokedCertificates_tag_S_Of_tag_oldret;
8812}
8813ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
8814ret += revokedCertificates_tag_for_oldret;
8815}
8816ret += revokedCertificates_tag_oldret;
8817}
8818ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
8819ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8820}
8821if((data)->crlExtensions){
8822size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
8823ret = 0;
8824ret += length_Extensions((data)->crlExtensions);
8825ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
8826ret += Top_tag_oldret;
8827}
8828ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
8829return ret;
8830}
8831
8832int ASN1CALL
8833copy_TBSCRLCertList(const TBSCRLCertList *from, TBSCRLCertList *to)
8834{
8835memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
8836{ int ret;
8837ret = der_copy_octet_string(&(from)->_save, &(to)->_save);
8838if (ret) goto fail;
8839}
8840if((from)->version) {
8841(to)->version = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->version));
8842if((to)->version == NULL) goto fail;
8843if(copy_Version((from)->version, (to)->version)) goto fail;
8844}else
8845(to)->version = NULL;
8846if(copy_AlgorithmIdentifier(&(from)->signature, &(to)->signature)) goto fail;
8847if(copy_Name(&(from)->issuer, &(to)->issuer)) goto fail;
8848if(copy_Time(&(from)->thisUpdate, &(to)->thisUpdate)) goto fail;
8849if((from)->nextUpdate) {
8850(to)->nextUpdate = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->nextUpdate));
8851if((to)->nextUpdate == NULL) goto fail;
8852if(copy_Time((from)->nextUpdate, (to)->nextUpdate)) goto fail;
8853}else
8854(to)->nextUpdate = NULL;
8855if((from)->revokedCertificates) {
8856(to)->revokedCertificates = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->revokedCertificates));
8857if((to)->revokedCertificates == NULL) goto fail;
8858if((((to)->revokedCertificates)->val = malloc(((from)->revokedCertificates)->len * sizeof(*((to)->revokedCertificates)->val))) == NULL && ((from)->revokedCertificates)->len != 0)
8859goto fail;
8860for(((to)->revokedCertificates)->len = 0; ((to)->revokedCertificates)->len < ((from)->revokedCertificates)->len; ((to)->revokedCertificates)->len++){
8861if(copy_CertificateSerialNumber(&(&((from)->revokedCertificates)->val[((to)->revokedCertificates)->len])->userCertificate, &(&((to)->revokedCertificates)->val[((to)->revokedCertificates)->len])->userCertificate)) goto fail;
8862if(copy_Time(&(&((from)->revokedCertificates)->val[((to)->revokedCertificates)->len])->revocationDate, &(&((to)->revokedCertificates)->val[((to)->revokedCertificates)->len])->revocationDate)) goto fail;
8863if((&((from)->revokedCertificates)->val[((to)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions) {
8864(&((to)->revokedCertificates)->val[((to)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions = malloc(sizeof(*(&((to)->revokedCertificates)->val[((to)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions));
8865if((&((to)->revokedCertificates)->val[((to)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions == NULL) goto fail;
8866if(copy_Extensions((&((from)->revokedCertificates)->val[((to)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions, (&((to)->revokedCertificates)->val[((to)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions)) goto fail;
8867}else
8868(&((to)->revokedCertificates)->val[((to)->revokedCertificates)->len])->crlEntryExtensions = NULL;
8869}
8870}else
8871(to)->revokedCertificates = NULL;
8872if((from)->crlExtensions) {
8873(to)->crlExtensions = malloc(sizeof(*(to)->crlExtensions));
8874if((to)->crlExtensions == NULL) goto fail;
8875if(copy_Extensions((from)->crlExtensions, (to)->crlExtensions)) goto fail;
8876}else
8877(to)->crlExtensions = NULL;
8878return 0;
8879fail:

9405size_t Top_Tag_nlen = Top_Tag_olen + sizeof(*((data)->val));
9406if (Top_Tag_olen > Top_Tag_nlen) { e = ASN1_OVERFLOW; goto fail; }
9407Top_Tag_olen = Top_Tag_nlen;
9408Top_Tag_tmp = realloc((data)->val, Top_Tag_olen);
9409if (Top_Tag_tmp == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
9410(data)->val = Top_Tag_tmp;
9411e = decode_AccessDescription(p, len, &(data)->val[(data)->len], &l);
9412if(e) goto fail;
9413p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
9414(data)->len++;
9415len = Top_Tag_origlen - ret;
9416}
9417ret += Top_Tag_oldret;
9418}
9419if ((data)->len > 2147483647) {
9420e = ASN1_MAX_CONSTRAINT; goto fail;
9421}
9422if ((data)->len < 1) {
9423e = ASN1_MIN_CONSTRAINT; goto fail;
9424}
9425len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
9426}
9427if(size) *size = ret;
9428return 0;
9429fail:
9430free_AuthorityInfoAccessSyntax(data);
9431return e;
9432}
9433
9434void ASN1CALL
9435free_AuthorityInfoAccessSyntax(AuthorityInfoAccessSyntax *data)
9436{
9437while((data)->len){
9438free_AccessDescription(&(data)->val[(data)->len-1]);
9439(data)->len--;
9440}
9441free((data)->val);
9442(data)->val = NULL;
9443}

9445size_t ASN1CALL
9446length_AuthorityInfoAccessSyntax(const AuthorityInfoAccessSyntax *data)
9447{
9448size_t ret = 0;
9449{
9450size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
9451unsigned int n_Top_tag;
9452ret = 0;
9453for(n_Top_tag = (data)->len; n_Top_tag > 0; --n_Top_tag){
9454size_t Top_tag_for_oldret = ret;
9455ret = 0;
9456ret += length_AccessDescription(&(data)->val[n_Top_tag - 1]);
9457ret += Top_tag_for_oldret;
9458}
9459ret += Top_tag_oldret;
9460}
9461ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
9462return ret;
9463}

9465int ASN1CALL
9466copy_AuthorityInfoAccessSyntax(const AuthorityInfoAccessSyntax *from, AuthorityInfoAccessSyntax *to)
9467{
9468memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
9469if(((to)->val = malloc((from)->len * sizeof(*(to)->val))) == NULL && (from)->len != 0)
9470goto fail;
9471for((to)->len = 0; (to)->len < (from)->len; (to)->len++){
9472if(copy_AccessDescription(&(from)->val[(to)->len], &(to)->val[(to)->len])) goto fail;
9473}
9474return 0;
9475fail:
9476free_AuthorityInfoAccessSyntax(to);
9477return ENOMEM;
9478}

9496encode_ProxyPolicy(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const ProxyPolicy *data, size_t *size)
9497{
9498size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
9499size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
9500int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
9501
9502/* policy */
9503if((data)->policy) {
9504size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
9505ret = 0;
9506e = der_put_octet_string(p, len, (data)->policy, &l);
9507if (e) return e;
9508p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
9509
9510e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_OctetString, &l);
9511if (e) return e;
9512p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
9513
9514ret += Top_tag_oldret;
9515}
9516/* policyLanguage */
9517{
9518size_t Top_tag_oldret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = ret;
9519ret = 0;
9520e = der_put_oid(p, len, &(data)->policyLanguage, &l);
9521if (e) return e;
9522p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
9523
9524e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_OID, &l);
9525if (e) return e;
9526p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
9527
9528ret += Top_tag_oldret;
9529}
9530e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, CONS, UT_Sequence, &l);
9531if (e) return e;
9532p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
9533
9534*size = ret;
9535return 0;

9538int ASN1CALL
9539decode_ProxyPolicy(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, ProxyPolicy *data, size_t *size)
9540{
9541size_t ret = 0;
9542size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
9543int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
9544
9545memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
9546{
9547size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
9548Der_type Top_type;
9549e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
9550if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
9551if(e) goto fail;
9552p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
9553Top_oldlen = len;
9554if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
9555len = Top_datalen;
9556{
9557size_t policyLanguage_datalen, policyLanguage_oldlen;
9558Der_type policyLanguage_type;
9559e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &policyLanguage_type, UT_OID, &policyLanguage_datalen, &l);
9560if (e == 0 && policyLanguage_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
9561if(e) goto fail;
9562p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
9563policyLanguage_oldlen = len;
9564if (policyLanguage_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
9565len = policyLanguage_datalen;
9566e = der_get_oid(p, len, &(data)->policyLanguage, &l);
9567if(e) goto fail;
9568p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
9569len = policyLanguage_oldlen - policyLanguage_datalen;
9570}
9571{
9572size_t policy_datalen, policy_oldlen;
9573Der_type policy_type;
9574e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &policy_type, UT_OctetString, &policy_datalen, &l);
9575if (e == 0 && policy_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
9576if(e) {
9577(data)->policy = NULL;
9578} else {
9579(data)->policy = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->policy));
9580if ((data)->policy == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
9581p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
9582policy_oldlen = len;
9583if (policy_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
9584len = policy_datalen;
9585e = der_get_octet_string(p, len, (data)->policy, &l);
9586if(e) goto fail;
9587p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
9588len = policy_oldlen - policy_datalen;
9589}
9590}
9591len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
9592}
9593if(size) *size = ret;
9594return 0;
9595fail:
9596free_ProxyPolicy(data);
9597return e;
9598}

9608}

9691{
9692size_t ret = 0;
9693size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
9694int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
9695

9698size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
9699Der_type Top_type;
9700e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_Sequence, &Top_datalen, &l);
9701if (e == 0 && Top_type != CONS) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
9702if(e) goto fail;
9703p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
9704Top_oldlen = len;
9705if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
9706len = Top_datalen;
9707{
9708size_t pCPathLenConstraint_datalen, pCPathLenConstraint_oldlen;
9709Der_type pCPathLenConstraint_type;
9710e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &pCPathLenConstraint_type, UT_Integer, &pCPathLenConstraint_datalen, &l);
9711if (e == 0 && pCPathLenConstraint_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }

9714} else {
9715(data)->pCPathLenConstraint = calloc(1, sizeof(*(data)->pCPathLenConstraint));
9716if ((data)->pCPathLenConstraint == NULL) { e = ENOMEM; goto fail; }
9717p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
9718pCPathLenConstraint_oldlen = len;
9719if (pCPathLenConstraint_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
9720len = pCPathLenConstraint_datalen;
9721e = der_get_unsigned(p, len, (data)->pCPathLenConstraint, &l);
9722if(e) goto fail;
9723p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
9724len = pCPathLenConstraint_oldlen - pCPathLenConstraint_datalen;
9725}
9726}
9727e = decode_ProxyPolicy(p, len, &(data)->proxyPolicy, &l);
9728if(e) goto fail;
9729p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
9730len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;

9734fail:
